Name: Schaefer 2018 Atlas
Description:
This atlas provides a labeling of cortical voxels in the MNI152
space, see Schaefer et al. (2018).
ReferencesAndLinks: A, Kong R, Gordon EM, Laumann TO, Zuo XN, Holmes AJ, Eickhoff SB, Yeo BTT. Local-Global parcellation of the human cerebral cortex from intrinsic functional connectivity MRI, Cerebral Cortex, 29:3095-3114, 2018
